.TH GPSD_NMEA 1 
.SH NAME
gpsd_nmea.sh - switches your gpsd to NMEA mode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B gpsdrive [options]


This is needed for some Gps-Receivers with SIF Chipüset. If you don't
switch them into NMEA mode the position will lag about 5-10 seconds
behind the reality.

